description: Viktor Rom and Devin Franco have a bit of a history on Lucas Entertainment: Viktor led Devin’s raw orgy, and the King of All Alpha Tops wanted another go ever since. Something about Devin’s sweet, all-American demeanor makes Viktor want to demolish him. He does that here, by tearing into Devin with an unforgettable fisting session.
title: Viktor Rom Invades And Fists Devin Franco
